ie II Manual.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPRABLP-90787_7447.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-Overview.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPRABLP-90787_7448.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-Range-Specs.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPRABLP-90787_55133.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-UN36N-Spec-Sheet.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPRABLP-90787_10453.jpg\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Oven-Icon-Functions.jpg</a></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab mod-last\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> </div> </div> \", \"Option1 Name\": \"Color\", \"Option1 Value\": \"RAL\", \"Option2 Name\": \"Trim\", \"Option2 Value\": \"Burnished\", \"Option3 Name\": \"Gas Type\", \"Option3 Value\": \"Liquid Propane\", \"Option4 Name\": \"Oven Door Type\", \"Option4 Value\": \"Triple Glass Door\", \"Google Shopping / Google Product Category\": \"Home & Garden > Household Appliances\", \"Google Shopping / Gender\": \"Unisex\", \"Google Shopping / Age Group\": \"Adult\", \"Google Shopping / MPN\": \"8051202542005\", \"Google Shopping / Condition\": \"New\", \"Google Shopping / Custom Product\": \"\", \"Google Shopping / Custom Label 0\": \"\", \"Google Shopping / Custom Label 1\": \"\", \"Google Shopping / Custom Label 2\": \"\", \"Google Shopping / Custom Label 3\": \"\", \"Google Shopping / Custom Label 4\": \"\"}, {\"Variant Name\": \"IL