eturn policy, please contact our support team.            <p>Please note the shipping times are based on current market conditions and are subject to change without notice</p> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_manuals-warranty\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab mod-last\\\" data-slug=\\\"manuals-warranty\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_manuals-warranty\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Manuals/Warranty</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_manuals-warranty\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_manuals-warranty\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <div><ul><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_4454.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Cleaning &amp; Maintenance.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_4213.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">ILVE USA Brochure.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_6907.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">ILVE USA Nostalgie Order Form.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_7597.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">ILVE-Warranty.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_4215.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie II Manual.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_7447.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-Overview.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_7448.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-Range-Specs.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_55133.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-UN36N-Spec-Sheet.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FNMPWHG-90787_10453.jpg\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Oven-Icon-Functions.jpg</a></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> <h3 class