awer</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Timer</th><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Rotisserie</th><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Soft Close Door</th><td>Yes</td></tr><tr><th scope=\\\"row\\\">Gas Conversion Kit Included</th><td>Yes</td></tr></table> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_shipping-returns\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" data-slug=\\\"shipping-returns\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_shipping-returns\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Shipping/Returns</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_shipping-returns\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_shipping-returns\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">            Please review Castle &amp; Cabana's <strong>Return, Refund, Exchange</strong> and <strong>Shipping Policies</strong> carefully, as certain brands may have specific terms that differ from our general store policies.            <br/><br/>            For detailed information, please refer to the following sections:            <br/>            1. <strong><a href=\\\"/pages/refund-and-return-policy\\\">Refund and Return Policy</a></strong> <br/>            2. <strong><a href=\\\"/pages/shipping-policy\\\">Shipping Policy</a></strong> <br/><br/>            If you have any questions or require further clarification, our team is happy to assist you. Kindly contact us at: <strong><a href=\\\"mailto:sales@castleandcabana.com\\\">sales@castleandcabana.com</a></strong> <br/><br/> <strong>Note</strong>: Some items are available for pre-order with an estimated delivery time of 90-120 days, including custom-made products such as select sauna cabins, luxury appliances, and other special-order items. Other products may have shorter shipping times of 15-45 days, while most items are in stock and ready to ship within 1-2 business days. For more information about specific shipping timelines or our return policy, please contact our support team.            <p>Please note the shipping times are based on current market conditions and are subject to change without notice</p> </div> </div> <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_manuals-warranty\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab mod-last\\\" data-slug=\\\"manuals-warranty\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_manuals-warranty\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Manuals/Warranty</span> </span></h3> <div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_manuals-warranty\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_manuals-warranty\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\"> <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"> <div><ul><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_4454.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Cleaning &amp; Maintenance.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_4213.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">ILVE USA Brochure.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_6907.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">ILVE USA Nostalgie Order Form.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_7597.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">ILVE-Warranty.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_4215.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie II Manual.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_7447.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-Overview.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_7448.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-Range-Specs.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-90787_55133.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Nostalgie-II-UN36N-Spec-Sheet.pdf</a></li><li><i></i> <a href=\\\"/cdn/shop/files/UN36FQNMPEGB-907